 du crépuscule</td><td align="left" valign="center">诗集</td></tr><tr><td align="left" valign="center"><b>1838</b></td><td width="173" height="0" align="left" valign="center" colspan="4">《吕布拉斯》</td><td width="138" align="left" valign="center">Ruy Blas</td><td width="39" align="left" valign="center">剧本</td></tr><tr><td align="left" valign="center"><b>1853</b></td><td width="173" height="0" align="left" valign="center" colspan="4">《<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%83%A9%E7%BD%9A%E9%9B%86">惩罚集</a>》</td><td width="138" align="left" valign="center">Les Chatiments</td><td width="40" align="left" valign="center">诗集</td></tr><tr><td align="left" valign="center"><b>1856</b></td><td width="173" height="0" align="left" valign="center" colspan="4">《<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%B2%89%E6%80%9D%E9%9B%86">沉思集</a>》</td><td width="138" align="left" valign="center">Les Contemplations</td><td width="41" align="left" valign="center">诗集</td></tr><tr><td align="left" valign="center"><b>1862</b></td><td width="173" height="0" align="left" valign="center" colspan="4">《<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%82%B2%E6%83%A8%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C">悲惨世界</a>》</td><td width="138" align="left" valign="center">Les Miserables</td><td width="42" align="left" valign="center">小说</td></tr><tr><td align="left" valign="center"><b>1866</b></td><td width="173" height="0" align="left" valign="center" colspan="4">《<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%B5%B7%E4%B8%8A%E5%8A%B3%E5%B7%A5">海上劳工</a>》</td><td width="138" align="left" valign="center">Les Travailleurs de la mer</td><td width="43" align="left" valign="center">小说</td></tr><tr><td align="left" valign="center"><b>1869</b></td><td width="173" height="0" align="left" valign="center" colspan="4">《<a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%AC%91%E9%9D%A2%E4%BA%BA">笑面人</a>》</td><td width="138" align="left" valign="center">L’Homme qui Rit</td><td width="44" align="left" valign="center">小说</td></tr><tr><td align="left" valign="center"><b>1859-1883</b></td><td width="173" height="0" align="left" valign="center" colspan="4">《<a target=_blank href="/item/%E4%B8%96%E7%BA%AA%E4%BC%A0%E8%AF%B4">世纪传说</a>》</td><td width="138" align="left" valign="center">La Legende des siecles</td><td width="45" align="left" valign="center">诗集</td></tr><tr><td align="left" valign="center"><b>1874</b></td><td width="173" height="0" align="left" valign="center" colspan="4"><div class="para" label-module="para">《<a target=_blank href="/item/%E4%B9%9D%E4%B8%89%E5%B9%B4">九三年</a>》</div>
