<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/tashuo/authorcenter?authorId=b35c476324d0280a433cc826" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/962bd40735fae6cd74e152b707b30f2443a70f8a.jpg" /></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>文化学者罗志渊</strong>
<span>文化学者、资深媒体人、新媒体专家。</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
</div>
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=feba954e988a2d6f07e58090&lemmaId=&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" class="cover" target="_blank">
<img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/c8177f3e6709c93d42b0ba7c943df8dcd00054fe.jpg" data-width="497" data-height="356" class="cover-img">
<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_1ccc6d9.png"></div>
<p class="title">
罗志渊：《悲惨世界》中的信仰与革命
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=feba954e988a2d6f07e58090&lemmaId=&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
这部电影，除了震撼之外，就是感动！感动于法国大革命的悲情色彩。学生组织成起义军，以黑红相间的花为革命徽章，黑色代表黑夜即将过去，红色代表革命的激情。然而，这支起义军一开始得到民众支持，在与官方较量中，悬殊太大，民众隐藏起来不再支持学生起义军。最后以一个小孩的死去把情节推向高潮。</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2017-12-15</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like " data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">41</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-tashuoId="2d016776b0f1beb9e9267ebf">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/tashuo/authorcenter?authorId=222bebc5db0a5b24b0bd5e21" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/6609c93d70cf3bc756fb14c4da00baa1cd112a1b.jpg" /></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>写乎</strong>
<span>探究历史悬疑，挖掘地方风物</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
</div>
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=2d016776b0f1beb9e9267ebf&lemmaId=&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" class="cover" target="_blank">
<img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/50da81cb39dbb6fd1d3151980224ab18972b3721.jpg" data-width="1440" data-height="900" class="cover-img">
<div class="overlay"><img src="https://bkssl.bdimg.com/static/wiki-lemma/widget/lemma_content/mainContent/tashuo/img/overlay_1ccc6d9.png"></div>
<p class="title">
有人说雨果是玩弄女性的伪君子，那么他与那些女性有过来往？
</p></a>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=2d016776b0f1beb9e9267ebf&lemmaId=&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
然而就是这样一位被人敬仰的大师，却在现实生活中寻花问柳，纵欲放荡，对于男欢女爱的私生活十分放肆几乎无耻。他认为世界上最容易也最刺激的是与女人做爱，他曾经对布尔迪说过：“讲话使我费力；作一次讲演等于做爱三次！”说完之后，又补充说，“甚至是四次。”</a>
</p>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2017-11-17</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like " data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">116</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
<li class="tashuo-item J-item" data-tashuoId="bad7cf355422cf09e4e333c4">
<div class="tashuo-author">
<a href="/tashuo/authorcenter?authorId=38aea596f131747dce094c21" target="_blank">
<div class="ta-author-area"><span><img src="https://imgsa.baidu.com/baike/pic/item/5366d0160924ab18e312b42f3efae6cd7b890ba5.jpg" /></span></div>
<div class="ta-author-slogan-area">
<strong>流金岁月</strong>
<span>有趣有料的资讯，尽在流金岁月</span>
</div>
<i></i></a>
</div>
<div class="no-cover">
<p class="title">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=bad7cf355422cf09e4e333c4&lemmaId=&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
雨果从未到过中国，却对中国一往情深，原来是因为一句贺词
</a>
</p>
<p class="abstract">
<a href="/tashuo/browse/content?id=bad7cf355422cf09e4e333c4&lemmaId=&fromLemmaModule=pcBottom" target="_blank">
“法兰西的莎士比亚”，创作过《巴黎圣母院》，《悲惨世界》等一系列脍炙人口的著作的大文豪雨果一生都与中国结下了不解之缘。当圆明园被英法联军...</a>
</p>
</div>
<div class="tashuo-operator">
<span class="tashuo-publish-date">2017-09-22</span><span class="tashuo-like J-like " data-isvote="0"><i></i><strong class="J-number">27</strong></span>
</div>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
